## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's alert feature, which uses Prophet machine learning to detect anomalies in product metrics. It covers three types of alerts (automatic, custom, and smart), how to configure them, and how alerts are delivered via email when metrics fall outside expected confidence intervals.

